description: Request a new sender ID that doesn't require registration.

parameters.name: SenderId
parameters.description: The sender ID string to request.

parameters.name: IsoCountryCode
parameters.description: The two-character code, in ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 format, for the country or region.

parameters.name: MessageTypes
parameters.description: The type of message. Valid values are TRANSACTIONAL for messages that are critical or time-sensitive and PROMOTIONAL for messages that aren't critical or time-sensitive. (string) ---

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: An array of tags (key and value pairs) to associate with the sender ID. (dict) --- The list of tags to be added to the specified topic. The key identifier, or name, of the tag. The string value associated with the key of the tag.

nested_params.name: Key
nested_params.description: The key identifier, or name, of the tag.

nested_params.name: Value
nested_params.description: The string value associated with the key of the tag.

parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: Unique, case-sensitive identifier that you provide to ensure the idempotency of the request. If you don't specify a client token, a randomly generated token is used for the request to ensure idempotency. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

nested_items.name: SenderIdArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) associated with the SenderId.

nested_items.name: SenderId
nested_items.description: The sender ID that was requested.

nested_items.name: IsoCountryCode
nested_items.description: The two-character code, in ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 format, for the country or region.

nested_items.name: MessageTypes
nested_items.description: The type of message. Valid values are TRANSACTIONAL for messages that are critical or time-sensitive and PROMOTIONAL for messages that aren't critical or time-sensitive.

nested_items.name: MonthlyLeasingPrice
nested_items.description: The monthly price, in US dollars, to lease the sender ID.

nested_items.name: DeletionProtectionEnabled
nested_items.description: By default this is set to false. When set to true the sender ID can't be deleted.

nested_items.name: Registered
nested_items.description: True if the sender ID is registered.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: An array of tags (key and value pairs) to associate with the sender ID.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: The key identifier, or name, of the tag.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: The string value associated with the key of the tag.
